[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0240","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0240.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0683","title":"Network Associates Gauntlet Firewall 5.0 ICMP Packet 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Network Associates Gauntlet Firewall 5.0 在处理异常格式的 ICMP 数据包时存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标防火墙发送特制的畸形 ICMP 报文，触发异常的报文处理流程，导致防火墙服务崩溃或停止响应，从而阻断正常网络流量通过。该漏洞直接影响 Gauntlet Firewall 5.0 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0683"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.410","remediation":"Network Associates Gauntlet Firewall 5.0 已停止技术支持，官方不再发布安全补丁。建议立即升级至仍在支持周期内的现代防火墙产品。如需临时缓解，可在网络边界 ACL 中配置丢弃畸形 ICMP 报文（如分片 ICMP、长度异常 ICMP 等），并限制 ICMP 速率，减少拒绝服务攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1029","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/556","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19441","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0683.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0683","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0683.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0683.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3834-9q92-mj44/GHSA-3834-9q92-mj44.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0683.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e2ff807e9fd18d30d388cc2c559c111ff993a143/1999.tsv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0683.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0240.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0240.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0240.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0972","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0972.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1130","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server JHTML 文件源码泄露漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 3.5.1及3.6版本中搜索引擎的默认配置存在信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过构造特制的搜索请求，利用HTML-tocrec-demo1.pat模式文件读取服务器上JHTML文件的源代码，导致敏感信息（如数据库连接参数、业务逻辑配置等）泄露。该漏洞影响Netscape Enterprise Server多个版本，攻击复杂度较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1130"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:47.070","remediation":"Netscape Enterprise Server 已停止维护且不再提供安全更新。建议立即迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server、Nginx 或 IIS）。作为临时缓解措施，可删除或重命名默认搜索配置中的 HTML-tocrec-demo1.pat 模式文件，并限制对搜索功能的访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93346448121208&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93337389603117&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/559","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19443"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0972.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0972.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1014","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1014.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1227","title":"Ethereal 数据包捕获文件本地符号链接攻击任意文件写入漏洞","description":"Ethereal（现更名为 Wireshark）网络封包分析工具在保存捕获文件时未能正确处理符号链接（symlink），存在不安全的临时文件释放漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在目标系统上预设恶意的符号链接，诱使 Ethereal 进程将捕获数据写入攻击者指定的任意文件路径，从而覆盖系统关键文件或用户数据。该漏洞攻击条件简单，本地用户即可利用，影响所有使用 Ethereal 保存数据包捕获文件的场景，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1227"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:59.377","remediation":"该漏洞存在于 Ethereal 在写入数据包捕获文件时未检查符号链接，攻击者可提前创建指向任意系统文件的符号链接，诱使 Ethereal 覆盖目标文件。建议立即升级至 Ethereal 0.8.0 或更高版本（该版本已修复符号链接跟随问题），或直接迁移至 Wireshark（Ethereal 的更名后继项目，默认不存在此漏洞）。临时缓解措施：避免以 root 权限运行 Ethereal，将捕获文件输出到专用目录并确保该目录不允许非信任用户写入，同时设置严格的 umask 限制文件权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ethereal.com/lists/ethereal-dev/199907/msg00126.html","http://www.ethereal.com/lists/ethereal-dev/199907/msg00130.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3334","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1227.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1227","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1227.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1227.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fx42-9wp5-842h/GHSA-fx42-9wp5-842h.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87548/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1227.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000713.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1014.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0276","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0276.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0700","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Phone Dialer 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 的 Phone Dialer（dialer.exe）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可通过向 dialer.ini 配置文件写入特制的畸形拨号条目，在程序解析该条目时触发缓冲区溢出，导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及所有 Service Pack 版本，攻击者需具备本地或远程写入 dialer.ini 文件的能力。成功利用后可获取目标系统控制权。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0700"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:52.550","remediation":"升级至 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a (SP6a) 或安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-037 提供的补丁。如无法升级，通过 NTFS 权限限制 dialer.ini 文件仅允许 Administrators 组写入，并移除 dialer.exe 的 Everyone 执行权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ237185","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-026","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19440","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0700.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0700","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0700.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0700.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-256c-v65p-vvfh/GHSA-256c-v65p-vvfh.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0700.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--9d37c81c-28be-4e85-a09d-7f39454834f2.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0276.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0492","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0492.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0770","title":"Check Point Firewall-1 非SYN连接超时拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Check Point Firewall-1 存在拒绝服务漏洞。该防火墙对以 ACK 等非 SYN 数据包开始的连接设置了过长的超时时间，远程攻击者可通过向无法响应的目标系统发送大量此类连接请求，耗尽防火墙会话表资源，导致无法处理正常连接请求。该漏洞影响 Firewall-1 3.0 及 4.0 版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0770"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.327","remediation":"升级 Check Point Firewall-1 至 4.1 及以上版本，该版本修复了非 SYN 包长超时问题，引入了正确的 TCP 状态跟踪机制。如无法升级，可在防火墙上手动调低非 SYN 连接的超时阈值，并限制单源 IP 的并发连接数，同时部署 ingress 过滤以阻断伪造源地址的攻击流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1027","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/549","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19436"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0492.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0924","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0924.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1078","title":"WS_FTP Pro 配置文件口令弱加密漏洞","description":"WS_FTP Pro 6.0 在初始化文件 ws_ftp.ini 中采用弱加密算法存储用户口令，攻击者在获取该配置文件后即可轻易解密出明文口令，进而获取系统登录权限。该漏洞利用难度较低，无需特殊权限即可利用，对受影响系统的机密性和完整性构成严重威胁。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1078"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:40.527","remediation":"升级 WS_FTP Pro 至 6.5 或更高版本，该版本已修复密码弱加密问题；鉴于 WS_FTP Pro 已停止维护且不再有安全更新，建议迁移至支持现代安全凭据存储的 FTP/SFTP 客户端（如 FileZilla 或 WinSCP），避免在配置文件中以任何形式明文或弱加密保存密码。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ntbugtraq.com/default.asp?pid=36&sid=1&A2=ind9907&L=ntbugtraq&D=0&P=10370&F=P","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/547","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1078","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-10xx/CVE-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/2d2ea2d13a3a7facfa195486d4f9782c62a06518/1999/CVE-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1078.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1078.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0924.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0868","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0868.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1017","title":"Seattle Labs Emurl 邮件附件脚本执行漏洞","description":"Seattle Labs Emurl 2.0 及更早版本存在不安全存储漏洞，程序将电子邮件附件存入启用了脚本执行的目录中，攻击者可通过发送包含恶意 ASP 文件附件的邮件触发该漏洞，当收件人打开邮件时 ASP 脚本自动执行，导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 Seattle Labs Emurl 系列邮件客户端，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1017"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-28T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.843","remediation":"在邮件附件存储目录中禁用脚本执行权限，将附件保存目录移出 Web 根目录或在该目录的 IIS 配置中移除 ASP/脚本映射。升级到 Emurl 2.0 以上版本，并配置附件目录无执行权限。如无法升级，可在 IIS 中将附件目录设置为禁止脚本执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93316253431588&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/544","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1017.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1017","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1017.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1017.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1017.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h7mf-q457-42rj/GHSA-h7mf-q457-42rj.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/544/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1017.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0868.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1684","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1684.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1018","title":"Linux Kernel IPChains IP 分片绕过安全漏洞","description":"Linux 内核 2.2.10 及更早版本中的 IPChains 防火墙组件在处理 IP 分片数据包时存在分片重组缺陷，在检查包头前未正确重组 IP 分片，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送多个偏移量为 0 的精心构造的 IP 分片，绕过防火墙过滤规则实现对内部网络的未授权访问。该漏洞影响 Linux 2.2.10 及之前版本内核，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1018"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.960","remediation":"升级至 Linux 内核 2.2.11 及以上版本（该版本已修复 IP 分片重组检查问题），或迁移至 2.4.x/2.6.x 等后续长期支持内核系列。若无法升级内核，可在防火墙规则中添加 `-f` 参数丢弃分片包作为临时缓解：`iptables -A INPUT -f -j DROP`。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93312523904591&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/543","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19301","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1018.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1018","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1018.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1018.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1018.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3xc5-vgfg-rqw3/GHSA-3xc5-vgfg-rqw3.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/543/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1018.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1684.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0406","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0406.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0710","title":"Squid cachemgr.cgi 未授权连接漏洞","description":"Squid 代理服务器在安装时将 cachemgr.cgi 管理脚本放置在公开 Web 目录下，导致远程攻击者无需认证即可直接访问该脚本，并利用其作为中转代理连接到任意内部或外部系统，造成信息泄露与未授权资源访问。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 5.2/6.0 及包含 Squid 2.2 之前版本的其他发行版，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0710"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:53.680","remediation":"立即从 Apache CGI 目录（如 /var/www/cgi-bin/）中移除 cachemgr.cgi 脚本，或通过 Apache 配置添加访问控制（Order deny,allow; Deny from all）仅允许受信 IP 访问。同时安装 Red Hat RHSA-1999-025 或 Debian DSA-576 提供的 Squid 安全更新包，升级至修复版本。如无法立即打补丁，可在 cachemgr.cgi 所在目录创建 .htaccess 文件添加 HTTP 基本认证作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://fedoranews.org/updates/FEDORA--.shtml","http://www.debian.org/security/2004/dsa-576","http://www.redhat.com/archives/fedora-announce-list/2005-May/msg00025.html","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA-1999-025.html","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA-2005-489.html","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/archives/rh52-errata-general.html#squid","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/2059","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2385","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20465"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0406.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0406.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0406.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0014","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0014.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0224","title":"Microsoft Windows NT Messenger Service 长用户名拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Messenger 服务在解析超长用户名时存在边界处理缺陷，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的超长用户名数据包，触发服务崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞利用方式简单，攻击者无需复杂工具即可通过标准网络协议发包实施攻击，影响 Windows NT 4.0 全版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0224"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-07-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.923","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 针对 Windows NT 4.0 的 Service Pack 5 (SP5) 或更高版本，该补丁修复了 Messenger Service 对畸形用户名处理不当的问题。对于已停止支持的旧系统，建议升级至 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本；若无法升级，可在服务管理器中禁用 \"Messenger\" 服务以消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0224","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/329","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0224.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0224.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0224","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0224.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0224.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0224.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0014.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0575","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0575.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0811","title":"Samba smbd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Samba 2.0.5 之前版本的 smbd 守护进程在处理畸形消息命令时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可向目标 Samba 服务发送特制的恶意消息包触发该漏洞，导致服务进程崩溃或实现本地权限提升，获取系统高权限。该漏洞影响所有 Samba 2.0.5 之前版本，CVSS 评分为 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0811"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.360","remediation":"升级 Samba 至 2.0.5 或更高版本，该版本修复了 smbd 进程处理畸形消息命令时的缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法升级，可在 smb.conf 中限制可访问 smbd 的源 IP 地址范围作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/536","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19428"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0575.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0808","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0808.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0810","title":"Samba nmbd 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Samba 2.0.5 的 NetBIOS 名称服务守护进程（nmbd）存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标发送特制的 NetBIOS 名称服务请求数据包，导致 nmbd 进程崩溃或进入死循环，从而停止响应正常的名称解析请求，造成网络服务中断。该漏洞影响 Samba 2.0.5 及之前版本，攻击复杂度低，无需用户交互。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0810"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.230","remediation":"升级 Samba 至 2.0.5 或更高版本（推荐 2.0.6），该版本修复了 nmbd 处理异常 NetBIOS 名称时陷入死循环或崩溃的问题。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙层面过滤 UDP 137 端口的入站 NetBIOS 名称服务请求作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0810"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0808.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0994","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0994.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1165","title":"GNU fingerd 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"GNU fingerd 1.37 存在权限处理不当漏洞，程序在访问用户信息前未能正确放弃特权，导致本地攻击者可通过两种方式利用：一是在 .fingerrc 文件中放置恶意程序获取 root 权限；二是利用 .plan、.forward 或 .project 文件的符号链接读取系统任意文件。该漏洞影响 GNU fingerd 1.37 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高，需手动修复或禁用 finger 服务。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1165"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:51.533","remediation":"建议立即升级 GNU fingerd 至 1.37 以上版本，该版本已修复权限提升漏洞。更推荐的方案是直接禁用 finger 服务（systemctl disable fingerd 或在 inetd/xinetd 配置中注释 finger 行），因为该服务在现代网络环境中已无必要且存在安全隐患。如必须使用，应限制 .plan/.forward/.project 等文件的写权限，禁止普通用户在这些文件中使用符号链接，并删除 .fingerrc 文件的可执行权限以防止恶意程序执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93268249021561&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/2478","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/535"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0994.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0408","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0408.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0721","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0/2000 Local Security Authority Subsystem LSA Request 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 的本地安全机构子系统（LSA）存在输入验证漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的畸形 LSA 请求，导致 LSA 服务崩溃，造成系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 和 Windows 2000 等版本，无需身份认证即可远程触发，危害等级高。Microsoft 官方已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0721"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.073","remediation":"安装 Microsoft Security Bulletin MS99-021 提供的安全更新补丁，或升级至 Windows 2000 Service Pack 1 及以上版本。如无法升级，可在防火墙层面过滤发往 LSA 服务的异常 TCP/UDP 流量作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ231457","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-049.shtml","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-020"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0408.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0306","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0306.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0692","title":"Cray Unicos Array Services 守护进程默认认证绕过漏洞","description":"Cray UNICOS 操作系统中的 Array Services 守护进程（arrayd）存在默认配置不当漏洞。该服务在默认安装情况下关闭了身份认证机制，导致远程攻击者无需任何凭证即可直接连接 arrayd 端口，并以 root 权限在目标系统上执行任意命令。攻击条件极低——只需目标开放 arrayd 服务且使用默认配置即可完成利用。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，影响 Cray UNICOS 系列操作系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0692"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.550","remediation":"升级 Cray Unicos 至厂商修复版本（如 8.0 及以上补丁级别），或修改 arrayd 配置文件启用认证（设置 require_authentication=yes）。如无法升级，使用 iptables 限制仅有信任管理节点可访问 arrayd 端口（默认 TCP/1050）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-052.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0692.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0692","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/479b29734109e75b43136719820cebdc00fad096/1999/CVE-1999-0692/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0692.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0692.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-g2hc-xmvw-hhph/GHSA-g2hc-xmvw-hhph.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0692.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--9e4ef6a4-48d0-4517-8dd9-a548963a1dd4.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0306.toml"}]